    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been a fantastic ride and is still in really solid shape\u2014perfect for daily commutes or weekend adventures! It runs smoothly and has been well-loved, so you\u2019re getting a great vehicle that\u2019s ready to hit the road. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know the next owner will love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
