      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning enthusiast is a well-sorted E92 M3, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies to deliver instantaneous throttle response up to its 8,400 RPM redline. Power is sent through a tactile 6-speed manual transmission to the rear wheels via a variable M differential lock. The chassis maintains its composure through aluminum multi-link suspension and functional Electronic Damper Control (EDC). Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the mechanical integrity of the valvetrain and induction system. A mechanically sound driver's car with excellent turn-in and a linear power band.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Ready for pickup.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
