      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise ZF 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-Differential lock. Mechanical highlights include a recently serviced VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The suspension geometry remains crisp with upgraded polyurethane bushings and Koni adjustable dampers. While the exterior shows honest character from spirited use, the drivetrain remains robust, offering the quintessential analog feedback and linear power delivery sought by purists.",
